query:
SELECT DISTINCT t.id, t.codigo, COUNT(e.id) as numEventos
FROM turmas t 
JOIN eventos e ON e.turmaId = t.id 
WHERE e.dataEvento IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY t.id, t.codigo
LIMIT 10
